---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Your Voice - Lewisham Your Party"
    description="Share an anonymous suggestion, concern, or idea with Lewisham Your Party through our local suggestion box."
>
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate p-8 md:p-16 pt-0 md:pt-0">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block mb-8 text-yp-red font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:underline">
                &larr; Back to Home
            </a>

            <section class="mb-10 md:mb-12">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-yp-red mb-4">Anonymous Suggestion Box</p>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-heading uppercase tracking-tighter inline-block border-b-8 border-yp-red pb-1 mb-6">
                    Your Voice
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed opacity-90 max-w-3xl mb-8">
                    If something in Lewisham needs attention, tell us. You do not need to be a member, and you do not need to give your name.
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                    <a href="#voice-form" class="inline-block bg-yp-red text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors text-center">
                        Send An Anonymous Submission
                    </a>
                    <a href="#how-it-works" class="inline-block border-4 border-yp-slate text-yp-slate font-bold py-4 px-6 uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-white transition-colors text-center">
                        How It Works
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] gap-10 items-start">
                <section id="how-it-works" class="order-2 xl:order-1 scroll-mt-10">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-1 gap-4 mb-8">
                        <div class="bg-yp-slate text-white p-5 border-t-8 border-yp-red shadow-lg">
                            <p class="font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-3">Anonymous First</p>
                            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                                Leave the contact field blank if you want to stay anonymous. Do not include identifying details in your message unless you want to.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white p-5 border-4 border-yp-slate shadow-lg">
                            <p class="font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm text-yp-red mb-3">Open To All</p>
                            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                                Residents, workers, students, neighbours, and anyone with a stake in Lewisham can use this box.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white p-5 border-4 border-yp-slate shadow-lg">
                            <p class="font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm text-yp-red mb-3">Volunteer Monitored</p>
                            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                                Messages are reviewed by the local organizing team. This is not an emergency service or a 24/7 casework inbox.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-yp-slate text-white p-8 shadow-xl">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4">What To Send</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
                            <p>Use this space for ideas, concerns, campaign tips, local issues, or things you think people in Lewisham are being ignored on.</p>
                            <p>If you want a reply, leave an email address. If you do not, leave it blank and your submission can stay anonymous.</p>
                            <p class="font-bold text-yp-cream">Please avoid sharing sensitive personal information about yourself or anyone else unless it is genuinely necessary.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section id="voice-form" class="order-1 xl:order-2 bg-white p-8 md:p-10 shadow-[10px_10px_0_0_rgba(34,56,63,1)] border-t-8 border-yp-red scroll-mt-10">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3">Send A Submission</h2>
                    <p class="text-base md:text-lg opacity-80 mb-8">
                        Short, direct, and specific messages are easiest for volunteers to act on.
                    </p>

                    <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                        <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="a31ca5cd-cd04-4c1a-a13a-72fc67f7de4f" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="https://lewishamyourparty.org.uk/voice-heard" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="New Your Voice submission - Lewisham YP" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="Lewisham Your Voice Box" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="Your Voice suggestion box" />
                        <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" class="hidden" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />

                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <label class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                                <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">What is this about? *</span>
                                <select name="Topic" required class="p-4 bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate border-4 border-transparent focus:border-yp-red focus:outline-none">
                                    <option value="">Choose a topic</option>
                                    <option>Local concern</option>
                                    <option>Idea or proposal</option>
                                    <option>Campaign tip</option>
                                    <option>Housing or rent</option>
                                    <option>Public services</option>
                                    <option>Street safety or transport</option>
                                    <option>Other</option>
                                </select>
                            </label>

                            <label class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                                <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Your connection to Lewisham</span>
                                <select name="Connection to Lewisham" class="p-4 bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate border-4 border-transparent focus:border-yp-red focus:outline-none">
                                    <option value="">Prefer not to say</option>
                                    <option>Resident</option>
                                    <option>Worker</option>
                                    <option>Student</option>
                                    <option>Local volunteer or organizer</option>
                                    <option>Regular visitor</option>
                                    <option>Supporter with an interest in Lewisham</option>
                                </select>
                            </label>

                            <label class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                                <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Area or postcode</span>
                                <input
                                    type="text"
                                    name="Area"
                                    placeholder="Optional, e.g. Catford or SE6"
                                    class="p-4 bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate border-4 border-transparent focus:border-yp-red focus:outline-none"
                                />
                            </label>

                            <label class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                                <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Email for reply</span>
                                <input
                                    type="email"
                                    name="email"
                                    placeholder="Leave blank to stay anonymous"
                                    class="p-4 bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate border-4 border-transparent focus:border-yp-red focus:outline-none"
                                />
                            </label>
                        </div>

                        <label class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">What should we hear? *</span>
                            <textarea
                                name="Message"
                                rows="10"
                                required
                                placeholder="Tell us what is happening, what should change, or what you think Lewisham organizers should pay attention to."
                                class="p-4 bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate border-4 border-transparent focus:border-yp-red focus:outline-none resize-y min-h-[240px]"
                            ></textarea>
                        </label>

                        <label class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="voice_consent" required class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 cursor-pointer" />
                            <span>
                                I understand this submission will be sent to Lewisham Your Party volunteers through Web3Forms, and if I want to remain anonymous I should avoid including personal details I would not want shared by email.
                            </span>
                        </label>

                        <div class="border-t-4 border-yp-slate pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold opacity-70">
                                Anonymous by default. Optional reply if you leave an email.
                            </p>
                            <button
                                type="submit"
                                class="bg-yp-red text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors cursor-pointer"
                            >
                                Send Your Voice
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
